
* Fix all the playdecks and OSD during video playback
* Log memory usage
* Auto-upgrade of Showtime
* Metadata priority order
* Fix list focus when destroying item via context menu
* Standardize view elements so .view plugins have something to lean on
* GLW .view plugins

---- view plugins ------------------

 - class -> path mapping

      home
      screensaver
      directory
      tracks (a list of tracks, such as Spotify playlist)
      album  (a list of tracks on the same album)
      albums (a list of albums)
      movies
      items
      images
      slideshow

 Which one is active is configurable somewhere and results in

  $ui.viewpath.home -> URL
  $ui.viewpath.screensaver -> URL
